snippet: New Caledonia, ranked just 155th in the world, defeated defending champion New Zealand, 2-0, in Honiara, Solomon Islands, to reach the final of the Oceania Nations Cup.
lead_paragraph: New Caledonia, ranked just 155th in the world, defeated defending champion New Zealand, 2-0, in Honiara, Solomon Islands, to reach the final of the Oceania Nations Cup.
